description: Creates a unique key that you can distribute to clients who invoke your API.

parameters.name: apiId
parameters.description: The ID for your GraphQL API.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: A description of the purpose of the API key.

nested_items.name: expires
nested_items.description: The time after which the API key expires. The date is represented as seconds since the epoch, rounded down to the nearest hour.

nested_items.name: deletes
nested_items.description: The time after which the API key is deleted. The date is represented as seconds since the epoch, rounded down to the nearest hour.
